{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Perry is a small robot with a big mission. Tasked with preparing a distant planet for human settlers, she must brave dangerous terrain and tumultuous weather to complete her mission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">During her mission, Perry learns about her fears, wants, and purpose through a heartfelt exploration of consciousness and the meaning of life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Prepare The Planet</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The atmosphere is toxic. Before humans can settle, much must be done, including planting seeds, testing dirt, and collecting scrap to prepare for all eventualities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432620/extras/Explore.gif?t=1736349024\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Brave Hostile Environments</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This planet will not be terraformed lightly: torrential storms and boulder fields threaten to blow Perry's mission off course.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432620/extras/Storms_-_Made_with_Clipchamp.gif?t=1736349024\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore Where Nobody Has Before</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the first entity to set foot (or rather, repulsor) on this planet there are secrets to be uncovered. Be sure to check every corner for undiscovered treasures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432620/extras/Cave.gif?t=1736349024\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3432620?t=1736349024","background_raw":"https://shared